description: Similar restrictions in counties Offaly and Laois have been lifted with immediate effect.
title: Kildare: Covid-19 restrictions extended for another two weeks
title_page: Kildare: Covid-19 restrictions extended for another two weeks - BBC News
maintext: Speaking after a meeting of the Irish government on Friday afternoon, Health Minister Stephen Donnelly said in recent days the number of cases has stabilised and is falling, however, he said they are still high.
